Enjoy the vibrations, ride the vibrations and make sure your voice is heard in these times of #love and chaos.  Rock out Speak out! ✌🏼✌🏾 #TelleInk #OneDay1Change #HearNoEvilMusicProject

hearNOevil #music project is about acknowledging the power and influence of music in our everyday lives across the world. In these times of love and chaos, what are the answers to a world that seems to be spinning out of control?  @oneday1change X @telleink will create a playlist daily that resonates with the times spreading positive vibes and staying away from violent and degrading lyrics. It's our "Rhythmic Prescription" to heal the world one playlist at a time. The lists will be available to stream or download on both @applemusic and @tidal to ensure everyone with a subscription access. #LOVE loud SEEK #balance CELEBRATE #diversity and let your freak flag fly!
